rComments: I think Professor Lee is one of those professors you just gotta give it to. He's a warm and helpful but doesn't make it easy on you. I think that if you do the readings and attend lectures tutorials you'll be able to pass it quiet easily. The only issue is, it's very reading intensive, so all lot of your grade is simply up to you. :) Overall- 810
One of the best profs I've had for political science.
HE IS REALLY AMAZING SUPER HELPFUL

Professor Lee is very clear, helpful, and overall a great instructor. What can be a very dry, and even difficult course, he manages to keep it interesting and very insightful. Covers the material extremely well, and always willing to help. 5/5 no doubt, highly recommend him!
Professor Daniel Lee is highly professional. Exams and assignments are fair. The lecture notes that he provides are excellent, and summarize the lecture and readings for that lecture very well.
